0.4: new note:

Form submit event: Broswer ----> Server (HTTP POST to server address: new_note)
HTTP Status Code: 302 - URL redirect: Server -----> Broswer (HTTP GET request - location: /notes)
                            (Broswer reloads "Notes" page)
HTTP requests: (main.css), (main.js),(data.json) Browser ----> Server


